# buildbot v0.8.8 setup
#
# ~buildbot/master/
#     BbConfig.py contains the master/slave password. Not in public git repo.
#     master.cfg  contains the usual buildbot config definitions and imports
#                 BbConfig.py
#
# ~buildbot/master/.git  contains git repository containing BbConfig.py ONLY
#
# ~/buildbot/master/.htpasswd  contains the htpasswd file supporting 
#         authentication for Forcing builds, Cancelling builds, and Deleting 
#         Pending builds .         
#
# ~/buildbot/master/builds/<builder_name>  contains the build logfiles made 
#         on the master in support of the named builder and build number.
#
